^ Claudia Eller (July 23, 2010). "Overture Films ends three-year run, hands off marketing and distribution to Relativity Media". Los Angeles Times. Tribune Publishing. 
^ Christian Lewis; Steve Donohue (September 4, 2006). "Starz Born Again as Movie Producer; Liberty Media Corp. acquired IDT Entertainment which was renamed as Starz Media". Multichannel News. Reed Business Information. Retrieved February 25, 2011 – via HighBeam Research. 
^ "A New Starz Is Born". PR Newswire. August 29, 2007. Retrieved April 21, 2015. 
