Description



Designed to be the ultimate fan experience, STARZ brings hit original series and movies right to your Xbox One. Plus, you can download the STARZ app to your smartphone or tablet and download full movies and shows to watch off-line, anytime, anywhere. Going somewhere without internet access? No problem. Select the shows and movies you want, download them ahead of time, and watch later at your leisure. That’s premium entertainment you can take with you, at an unbeatable price. 

If you’re already a STARZ subscriber, you can download the app on your Xbox One right now and enjoy it free. Or, subscribe to the STARZ app direct through the App Store or Google Play and try it free for 7 days (just $8.99/month after free trial). No other subscription to any other service is required. Comcast/Xfinity does not allow subscribers to log into the STARZ app at this time.
More




Available on


Xbox One



 











Version notes
Version number: Varies by device
Support for services migration and upgrades.
Improvements to stability and performance.
Various bug fixes and enhancements.




Features

Download – If you’re going to hit the road, you can download movies and shows to your smartphone or tablet and watch offline. That’s premium entertainment that allows you to watch how you want
Resume – You can pick up where you left of, even on your smartphone, tablet or any other supported device linked to the account
Playlist – Curate your own playlist by adding movies or original series so you can watch exactly what you want 
Favorites – See an actor or actress that you can watch over and over again? Add them to your favorites list and you’ll see all of the movies that they’re currently in on STARZ.
Full HD – Stream movies and shows in full 1080P high definition 











