6/8/2017
Unknown
Xbox


Great for watching STARZ original programming!


            This app is great for streaming. The movie selection isn't as extensive as Netflix, but everything is good. Old early 90s classics to newer movies. Where this app shines is in the STARZ original programming like Ash vs. Evil Dead, Black Sails and American Gods. No other place can you get these shows streaming in HD the night they air. They also have a pretty decent anime section. Probably close to 10 series but they're all good. Ghost in the Shell to the Dirty Pair. This app is worth it if you want to break the monotony of Netflix. Try STARZ and chill sometimes, you won't be disappointed. :)
        

